===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|aberen}}, from {{inh|en|ang|āberan||to bear, carry, carry away}}, from {{m|ang|ā-||away, out}}, {{m|ang|a-}} + {{m|ang|beran||to bear}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*uzberaną||to bear off, bring forth, produce}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*bʰer-||to bear, carry}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|a|bear}}. Cognate with {{cog|goh|irberan}}, {{cog|got|𐌿𐍃𐌱𐌰𐌹𐍂𐌰𐌽}}.

